Tags are short, reusable text descriptions that can be applied to plots or subplots when scoring.

2
00:00:10,366 --> 00:00:14,366
You can create new tags by select the Add Tag button in the Tags screen.

3
00:00:20,866 --> 00:00:24,866
Enter a label. This is the name of the tag.

4
00:00:28,200 --> 00:00:32,200
Select the Use button to see if the label is already in use.

5
00:00:33,566 --> 00:00:37,566
If the label name if free, then you can enter a short description.

6
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:44,500
Select the Confirm button to create the tag.

7
00:00:50,733 --> 00:00:54,733
The tag is now available when scoring
